      "_readme": "Fresh-spawn loadout (Expansion SpawnSettings.json). PATCH only these fields so the rest of the file (SpawnLocations, cooldowns, clothing pools) stays whatever the box + map/inventory sync manages, and an Expansion update that rewrites the baseline is inherited. UpperGear = knife + heatpack only (no rags/apple); Backpacks emptied so fresh spawns carry no bag. Re-applied by prestart every start. Sakhal-scoped (only live map; heatpack is for its cold) - promote the knife/backpack bits to mpmissions.common if more maps go live. Spawn stats are PINNED here (health 100 = full; energy/water 2500 each) because an Expansion baseline reset (m_Version bump) reverted SpawnEnergyValue/SpawnWaterValue to a low 500 default, making fresh spawns immediately hungry AND thirsty - pinning them means a future reset can't reintroduce that. 2500 buffers Sakhal's cold drain; lower toward ~1100/900 for a harder start.",
